quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ìi…ó…óo makko on Yuusufa:Ko an yo …ìinngel am, wata a hoy…óitan musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen koy…óol maa ngol, sakko …ìe faama ngol, …ìe haasido maa, …ìe fewjane fewjoore haasidaaku ma…ì…ìe. Pellet seytaane wonannde ne…ó…óanke ko ga√±o …ìanngin…óo ngayngu."
  12,6,"Ko wano yiiru-…óaa …óin koy…ói non, Joomi maa an Yuusufa su…ìoray maa, O anndine firo koy…ói, O timmina neema Annabaaku ngun e maa…óa, wano O timminira mo e baabiraa…ìe maa …ìen …ói…óo ado maa…óa: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko Anndu…óo tagu Makko ngun, √ëee√±u…óo e yiilde mbo."
  12,7,"Gom…óii wonii e kabaaru Yuusufa on e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen, taskuyeeji e waajuuji wonannde lanndotoo…ìe fii ma…ì…ìe …ìen."
  12,8,"Tuma nde musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen wi'unoo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe: "Pellet Ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto maun …ìuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe limoore, ko honno …ìe …ìurdinirta …ìe e dow mee…óen? Menen men yi'ii baaba'en e faljere …ìanngunde, tuma …ìe …ìurdinnoo …ìeya …ói…óo e dow amen ko aldaa e sabu fee√±u…óo."
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi wo…ó…óundi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, …ìe yi…óa on giggol timmungol, wonton …ìaawo …óen kuu…óe mon- warugol mo maa feragol mon- …óon yim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe, si on tuubi e junuubi mon …óin."
  12,10,"Gooto e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìen wi'i: Wata on waru Yuusufa, on wedduto mo ka ni…ìe woyndu yoga e setee…ìe rewoo…ìe …óon …ìen hocca-mo. Ko …óum …ìuri newaade diini warugol mo ngol, si on laatike siinu…ìe e ko wi'u…óon fii makko kon."
  12,11,"Nde …ìe fottanno pottingol mo, …ìe wi'ani ben ma…ì…ìe Yaaquuba: Ko an yo ben amen, ko he…ìu-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men yurmetee…ìe mo, me…óen reena mo e ko lorrota mo, ko men laa…ìanoo…ìe mo reenoo…ìe mo haa o ruttora kaa maa…óa kisal. Ko ha…óata maa acciditah mo e amen?"
  12,12,"Newnan-men yaltidugol e makko janngo, o √±aama, o fija. Menen ko men reenoo…ìe mo e kala lorra memoowo mo."
  12,13,"Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen: Min no sunina lam nde yahdoton e makko; tawde mi mu√±√±otaako sertugol e makko, mi…óo hulani mo wata saafaandu(boyeeru) √±aamu-mo ka welsindor-…óon e makko √±aamugol e fija."
  12,14,"∆Åe wi'ani baaben ma…ì…ìe: Pellet si saafaandu √±aamii Yuusufa e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe, haray ontuma ko men hayru…ìe …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere alah e mu'un; tawde men ha…óaali ndu e makko."